==Dutch==

===Adverb===
'''waarvoor'''

# [[what]]...[[for]]; [[wherefore]]; [[for]] [[which]]
#: '''''Waarvoor''' is dat?'' &mdash; Why is that? To what end is that?
#: '''''Waar''' is dit goed '''voor?''''' &mdash; What is this good for?
#: '''''Waarvoor''' doe je dat?'' &mdash; What are you doing that for?
#: ''Het gevaar '''waarvoor''' we ons moeten hoeden.'' &mdash; The danger which we need to beware of.

====Usage notes====
*This is a separable adverb. The likelihood of separation varies between regional dialect. Compare the following (meaning: "What's that for?"):
*: '''''Waarvoor''' dient dat?'' (usually the Netherlands)
*: '''''Waar''' dient dat '''voor'''?'' (usually Flanders)

